{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Enable Ukrainian students to take their GCSEs in Ukrainian",
        "additional_details": "We want the government to work with the Ukrainian community and education authorities to ensure that GCSE exams in Ukrainian are accessible and available to all eligible students.\r\n\r\nWe think this could:\r\n\r\n- Encourage the appreciation of Ukrainian language and culture\r\n- Promote diversity and inclusion in the education system\r\n- Support the integration of Ukrainian students into British society",
        "background": "We want the government to enable students to take their GCSE exams in Ukrainian. This could provide Ukrainian students with the opportunity to take exams in their native language.",
